</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='361000' id='t-361000'>I started a foundation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='363000' id='t-363000'>to bet on these good people doing good things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='365000' id='t-365000'>These leading, innovative, nonprofit folks,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='368000' id='t-368000'>who are using business skills in a very leveraged way</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='371000' id='t-371000'>to solve social problems.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='373000' id='t-373000'>People today we call social entrepreneurs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376000' id='t-376000'>And to put a face on it, people like Muhammad Yunus,</span>
