<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385000' id='t-385000'>But there's also a lot of people that you don't know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388000' id='t-388000'>Folks like Ann Cotton, who started a group called CAMFED in Africa,</span>
