<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425000' id='t-425000'>And a lot of this comes together in a philosophy of change</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429000' id='t-429000'>that I find really is powerful.</span>
