12:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>And you know, there's another adage in Hollywood,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713000' id='t-713000'>that nobody knows nothing about anything.</span>
